        "TileImage": "$($repository 856b2aa2-e224-48c3-b890-01fdf4dba6de).Image",
        "Description": "Tonight&apos;s the night. And it&apos;s going to happen again and again. Has to happen. Nice night. Helen West, she&apos;s presented as sweet and harmless, but her obsession with poisons is lethal. She craves control over life and death, experimenting with chemicals for thrills, not necessity. Frank Schmidt&apos;s death wasn&apos;t an accident, it was a consequence of her compulsion.\rShe&apos;s meticolous, sadistic and highly dangerous. She needs containment before more lives are lost",
